lead_paragraph: In one of the most bizarre scenarios imaginable at a major sporting event, top-ranked Notre Dame and Louisiana-Lafayette switched venues in the middle of their game due to a power outage.

headline.print_headline: No. 1 Notre Dame Moves Game After Power Outage
